review_text: Small park with a swingset, small playground, benches, and a bike rack.
Small intimate neighborhood park, with lots of shade. Perfect for toddlers and older kids.
Very quiet, away from the traffic and crowded areas. Has a fence, so one couldn't be too worried when the little ones are running around.

(Translated by Google) Quiet park. Too bad there is no fountain to drink.

(Original)
Parc tranquille. Dommage qu'il n'y ait pas de fontaine pour se désaltérer.
